{"type": "article", "id": 47709, "title": "模仿甲壳虫造型的吸音墙板，做墙面装饰也不错｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-11-28T23:26:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 39676, "name": "Sancal"}, {"id": 22454, "name": "MUT Design"}, {"id": 43582, "name": "ferm LIVING"}, {"id": 45877, "name": "Tsatsas"}, {"id": 45878, "name": "Marshall"}, {"id": 45879, "name": "Youngdo Choi"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 98, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171128194247ViF7ktLS0H9MTr5B.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; background-color: transparent} span.s4 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Beetle panel range by MUT Design for Sancal</h3><p>西班牙工作室 MUT Design 为家具品牌 Sancal 创造了一系列由甲虫壳启发的彩色吸音墙板，灵感源自一趟自然科学博物馆之旅。这一系列包括 12 种不同的设计，每种设计都由六种不同的面板形状组合而成。所有的设计都是为了模仿昆虫壳上的图案和颜色。然后只需要用橡木制成的支架将其固定在墙上就可以了。支架的颜色也是可选的，比如 Klein蓝、坚果色或是玫瑰色。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171128194321ZJPjDKBhtadAm7kl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.711506\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171128194321MTeARo6bm8pl4vUt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171128194321KOb1ga93evMw0prT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171128194322t95KWGNAjV6Zcoex.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.656937\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171128194322QhpcV82eUdbCwOKk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.732234\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171128194322b53Ci1ADVXzgOIls.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.031726\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2017/11/27/sancal-mut-design-fabric-acoustic-panels-look-like-beetles-promotion/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Braided Floor Basket (Set of 3) by ferm LIVING</h3><p>在丹麦家居设计品牌 ferm LIVING 2017 秋冬系列中，这款专为儿童设计的编织篮看着不错。它用手搓纸编织而成，分为大中小三个型号，不同尺寸的篮子边缘颜色不同，比如玫瑰色、浅灰色和灰绿色。造型简单，圆润的身材对于小孩子来说极具亲和力，适合放置在儿童房中，收纳小朋友的羊毛袜子、泰迪熊、积木以及各类玩具，提供收纳解决方案的同时，不失为一件小小的装饰物。三个一套售价 135 欧元，<a href=\"https://www.fermliving.com/webshop/shop/news-kids-aw17/braided-floor-basket-(set-of-3).aspx\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171128194417QJ5m84u9oRnKbXr2.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171128194417FqWi3VkQ0LYwosIy.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171128194418sZ1MKqOp7auP4roc.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171128194417YPkWulmVNg2vB40a.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171128194418Bydzw2OpRaPbUKNS.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.fermliving.com/webshop/shop/news-kids-aw17/braided-floor-basket-(set-of-3).aspx\" rel=\"nofollow\">ferm LIVING</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Marsh Backpack by Tsatsas</h3><p>创立于 2012 年的德国手工皮革品牌 Tsatsas ，强调设计和工艺，所有的包袋全部由手工制作而成，试图在美学和功能性之间找到平衡，休闲、正式场合皆有不同的选择。最新推出的这款 Marsh 背包，男女通用，手柄位于背包顶部，肩带可调节，提供小牛皮和柔软的磨砂皮革两种材质和 8 种不同的颜色可选。外部看似自然凹陷下去的形状很酷，且并不多见。它看起来很简单，但又带着有力的设计细节。售价 1400 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.tsatsas.com/collection_marsh.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171128194532QYAPc8jk1Jwl5NOR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333594\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171128194532j5ihKUpDZGg23Swf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171128194531ftxlesUyDduHTE3O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333669\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171128194532pPUHMTk0dwzcDB85.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711281945330hWciPoVaKrSyjYN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333669\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.tsatsas.com/collection_marsh.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tsatsas</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Wireless - Monitor Bluetooth Headphones by Marshall</h3><p>在音响器材领域口碑极好的 Marshall，今年推出了基于 Marshall Monitor 监听级耳机的无线蓝牙版本，在保留原有音质的同时，其拥有高达 30 小时的无线续航时间。这款耳机延续了品牌经常使用的黑金色系，黑色皮纹头带，黄铜细节点缀，搭配抢眼的白色 logo 在两边的耳罩上。售价 249 美元，<a href=\"https://www.marshallheadphones.com/mh_us_en/monitor-bluetooth\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711281947060Tet1PKu2VoDsBSq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171128194707IPxVK4sXgMmh5c0d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.221944\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171128194708rT5pIECPznJKRoaH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171128194710jF2DCEBJ4hVLxK1Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.983594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171128194711YJnHcRLBd9CxzvNX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.611260\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.marshallheadphones.com/mh_us_en/monitor-bluetooth\" rel=\"nofollow\">Marshall</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Still Teapot by ferm LIVING</h3><p>同样是来自 ferm LIVING 的产品，这款名为 Still 的茶壶，希望帮助用户重新回到传统的宁静的煮茶仪式的氛围中。它采用透明的有色吹制玻璃制成，容器中心的茶漏是茶壶的焦点，再加上顶部的玻璃盖，力求赋予茶壶整体“简单和平衡”的结构。按照设计师的说法，“我们只是想鼓励使用者能够多花一点时间，坐下来享受一杯香气满溢的茶，或是两杯。”售价 69 欧元，<a href=\"https://www.fermliving.com/webshop/shop/kitchen/still-teapot.aspx\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171128194757HyXtIVPS5BefxRLA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171128194757WPZ3rVCfAX9uHawo.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711281947587XNYSjmwKiTuMIt2.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171128194758vV9ZuwpHPe25JgXo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.fermliving.com/webshop/shop/kitchen/still-teapot.aspx\" rel=\"nofollow\">ferm LIVING</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Tape Measure by Youngdo Choi</h3><p>在使用卷尺时，你是不是经常会遇到一个问题，需要找只笔来标记一下，或是任何能够留下痕迹的东西。设计师 Youngdo Choi 在卷尺带口下方，加入了一个可伸缩铅笔的导线，可以标记测量值，从而解决这一不便之处。卷尺光滑圆润的盘状造型，简单又可爱，黑白两色的配色也赋予了卷尺当代审美的特性。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171128194846Sso8kgPnZ0zRurcF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171128194846SsW0IF9EURazkm16.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017112819484650cCMxwd2zXbAWVk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171128194846s6MElXgcB9p4GeUt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171128194847cQC8JL64huU3oeS5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}